Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.74,0:07:16.72,Flashback,TANAKA,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.01,0:07:19.48,Flashback,TANAKA,0000,0000,0000,,4,000 yen?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.91,0:07:22.08,Italics,TANAKA,0000,0000,0000,,My rival was stubborn.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.08,0:07:25.41,Italics,TANAKA,0000,0000,0000,,I felt his passion and determination \Nto acquire the eraser, no matter the cost.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.41,0:07:28.30,Italics,TANAKA,0000,0000,0000,,Battling against an opponent with\N unknown intentions and budget
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.30,0:07:30.82,Italics,TANAKA,0000,0000,0000,,is the charm of online auctions.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.18,0:07:33.78,Italics,TANAKA,0000,0000,0000,,However, I was determined.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.78,0:07:36.65,Italics,TANAKA,0000,0000,0000,,I input 4,100 yen.
