Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.54,0:08:02.07,Italics,TANAKA,0000,0000,0000,,It was as though I'd been \Narrested on false charges
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.07,0:08:03.94,Italics,TANAKA,0000,0000,0000,,and was desperately trying \Nto prove my own innocence
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.94,0:08:06.82,Italics,TANAKA,0000,0000,0000,,while the police presented more \Nand more physical evidence.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.82,0:08:09.64,Italics,TANAKA,0000,0000,0000,,I remember feeling that kind of despair.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.30,0:08:14.08,Italics,TANAKA,0000,0000,0000,,No, that's also an exaggeration and a lie.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.49,0:08:17.36,Italics,TANAKA,0000,0000,0000,,But it's true that I experienced \Na despair that's difficult to describe.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.80,0:08:20.18,Italics,TANAKA,0000,0000,0000,,That's when it happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.18,0:08:21.53,Flashback,BROTHER,0000,0000,0000,,I'm home.
