Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.05,0:08:54.55,Flashback,TANAKA,0000,0000,0000,,There was something I wanted to look up.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.94,0:08:57.00,Flashback,BROTHER,0000,0000,0000,,I told you not to touch my stuff!
