Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.18,0:09:05.60,sign_13000_209_Number_of_Items_,SIGN [blurry; hard to read],0000,0000,0000,,Number of Items: 1 \NFinal Price 100,000 yen
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.18,0:09:05.60,sign_13000_210_Begin_Transactio,BLUE BUTTON SIGN,0000,0000,0000,,Begin Transaction
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.18,0:09:05.60,sign_13000_211_Seller_Informati,SIGN,0000,0000,0000,,Seller Information {\c&Hc69c32&}ditch-11
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.18,0:09:06.21,Italics,TANAKA,0000,0000,0000,,It was me. I definitely won the auction.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.60,0:09:07.69,sign_13082_214_Begin_Transactio,BLUE BUTTON SIGN,0000,0000,0000,,Begin Transaction
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.60,0:09:07.69,sign_13082_215_Seller_Informati,SIGN,0000,0000,0000,,Seller Information
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.21,0:09:07.69,Italics,TANAKA,0000,0000,0000,,I had lost my mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.18,0:09:09.65,Flashback,STUDENT A,0000,0000,0000,,Let's play soccer.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.41,0:09:12.10,Flashback,STUDENT E,0000,0000,0000,,Let's sprint to the field.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.69,0:09:17.19,Italics,TANAKA,0000,0000,0000,,In Japan, a group of citizens \Nonce staged a revolution
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.19,0:09:20.33,Italics,TANAKA,0000,0000,0000,,due to their discontent \Nover the economic divide.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.33,0:09:24.20,sign_13435_221_What_is_the_Hyak,SIGN,0000,0000,0000,,What is the Hyakushou Ikki \NTenant Farmer Uprising? \NEdo Period \N{\c&H48c9be&}Tenant Farmers \N{\c&Hd7c554&}Feudal Lords
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.81,0:09:24.83,Italics,TANAKA,0000,0000,0000,,In this classroom, our teacher's efforts \Nto prevent the wealth gap from widening
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.83,0:09:29.14,Italics,TANAKA,0000,0000,0000,,produced a twisted backlash \Nin exactly one student.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.63,0:09:32.75,Italics,TANAKA,0000,0000,0000,,It wasn't an organized movement \Nlike an uprising or rebellion.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.75,0:09:35.05,Italics,TANAKA,0000,0000,0000,,It was a revolution brought \Nabout by just one student.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.46,0:09:38.60,Italics,TANAKA,0000,0000,0000,,I called it Tanaka's Revolution.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.34,0:09:42.10,Italics,TANAKA,0000,0000,0000,,Once again, I returned home \Nand messaged the seller
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.10,0:09:44.53,Italics,TANAKA,0000,0000,0000,,regarding the shipping\N address for the eraser.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.53,0:09:48.49,Italics,TANAKA,0000,0000,0000,,All that remained was to wait for \Nmy original Donraku eraser to arrive.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.27,0:09:58.66,sign_14129_230_Tanaka,BROWN SIGN,0000,0000,0000,,Tanaka
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.31,0:09:53.54,Italics,TANAKA,0000,0000,0000,,One week passed.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.93,0:09:57.64,Italics,TANAKA,0000,0000,0000,,One month passed.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.66,0:10:01.32,Italics,TANAKA,0000,0000,0000,,My original Donraku eraser had not arrived.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.65,0:10:04.86,Italics,TANAKA,0000,0000,0000,,I recalled the words \N"no refunds, no returns."
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.86,0:10:07.59,Italics,TANAKA,0000,0000,0000,,I realized now that there were \Nplenty of things I could have done.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.11,0:10:08.19,Flashback,HANDSOME,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Maki-chan, let's compare answers.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.59,0:10:12.22,Italics,TANAKA,0000,0000,0000,,But at the time, I was bound firmly \Nby the words "no refunds, no returns,"
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.19,0:10:11.38,Flashback,FIGHTER,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}You just want to copy her homework.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.41,0:10:11.38,Flashback,ARTIST,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}I always let you see my homework.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.24,0:10:14.10,Italics,TANAKA,0000,0000,0000,,and had no options.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.42,0:10:16.85,Italics,TANAKA,0000,0000,0000,,Besides, I consented \Nto bidding on the eraser.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.85,0:10:21.17,Italics,TANAKA,0000,0000,0000,,I had no right to demand compensation, \Nand I had nothing to return.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.84,0:10:26.49,Italics,TANAKA,0000,0000,0000,,Sato and the rest of my classmates \Nhad already lost interest in erasers.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.49,0:10:30.44,Italics,TANAKA,0000,0000,0000,,Third-year grade school \Nstudents grow up fast.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.56,0:10:36.12,Italics,TANAKA,0000,0000,0000,,And when my father reviewed \Nhis credit card statement,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.12,0:10:38.12,Italics,TANAKA,0000,0000,0000,,he beat me to a pulp.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.74,0:10:42.73,Italics,TANAKA,0000,0000,0000,,As he was beating me, \NI wondered whose fault this was.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.12,0:10:45.87,Italics,TANAKA,0000,0000,0000,,My teacher. My classmates.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.87,0:10:48.66,Italics,TANAKA,0000,0000,0000,,Sato. My brother. My father.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.66,0:10:50.95,Italics,TANAKA,0000,0000,0000,,The seller. The bidder.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.95,0:10:53.96,Italics,TANAKA,0000,0000,0000,,Me. My country. History.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.96,0:10:55.72,Italics,TANAKA,0000,0000,0000,,Civilization. The government.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.72,0:10:56.75,Italics,TANAKA,0000,0000,0000,,God.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.09,0:11:00.41,Italics,TANAKA,0000,0000,0000,,No matter how I looked at it, \Nit was clearly my fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.41,0:11:02.42,Italics,TANAKA,0000,0000,0000,,And if there was a loser \Nin this situation...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.73,0:11:04.32,Flashback,MOM,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Honey, honey!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.72,0:11:05.22,Italics,TANAKA,0000,0000,0000,,...it was me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.59,0:11:09.75,Italics,TANAKA,0000,0000,0000,,And so, Tanaka's Revolution ended.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.90,0:11:13.23,Italics,TANAKA,0000,0000,0000,,Returning to a previous topic,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.23,0:11:16.07,Italics,TANAKA,0000,0000,0000,,since then, I've come to despise \Nanything without a real form
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.07,0:11:17.64,Italics,TANAKA,0000,0000,0000,,as well as competing with others.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.64,0:11:18.52,Flashback,COWORKER F,0000,0000,0000,,Good night.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.52,0:11:20.19,Flashback,TANAKA,0000,0000,0000,,Good night.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.58,0:11:22.47,Italics,TANAKA,0000,0000,0000,,Games are meant to be played alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.47,0:11:25.29,Italics,TANAKA,0000,0000,0000,,All alone, battling against the developer.
